        },
        {
            "text": "The new version lets humanity off the hook, doesn't it, at least for the moment?",
            "created": "Tue, 06 Sep 2022 02:50:22 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/09/05/020943.html?title=revision#a025022",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "<b>A Private Club</b><br><br>After I learned<br>the secret handshake,<br>I saw it everywhere.",
                    "created": "Tue, 06 Sep 2022 02:51:27 GMT",
