                    "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/09/05/020943.html?title=revision#a025127"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "Seems like the shorter version gives a reader more space for deliberation. The older version puts a hand on the reader's shoulder, gives a squeeze, and says, \"Got it?\"",
            "created": "Tue, 06 Sep 2022 02:54:22 GMT",
            "permalink": "http://oldschool.scripting.com/KenSmith/2022/09/05/020943.html?title=revision#a025422"
        },
        {
            "text": "I suppose one of the things sentences do is have more or have less respect for the judgment and good sense of a reader.",
